OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FThe Northern Trust is proposing a
OL,7,Fmajor change in surgery, with
OL,8,Femergency procedures to be carried out
OL,9,Fat Antrim Area Hospital and planned
OL,10,Foperations only in the Causeway in
OL,11,FColeraine.
OL,13,FThey say that the re-configuration
OL,14,Fwill prevent a collapse of services,
OL,15,Fwhich happened in other hospitals.
OL,16,FHowever campaigners for The Causeway
OL,17,FHospital are concerned that the move
OL,18,Fwill further diminish provision in
OL,19,FColeraine and put pressure on other
OL,20,Fhospitals.
