OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FThe Northern Health and Social Care
OL,7,FTrust is launching a 14-week public
OL,8,Fconsultation on proposals to transform
OL,9,Fits general surgery services.
OL,11,FAt a meeting of the Board of the
OL,12,FNorthern Trust on Thursday 22 August,
OL,13,Fthe Trust's senior management outlined
OL,14,Fan evidence-based case for change,
OL,15,Fproposing to centralise emergency
OL,16,Fgeneral surgery at Antrim Area
OL,17,FHospital, while the majority of
OL,18,Felective general surgery (planned
OL,19,Fsurgery and procedures) will take
OL,20,Fplace at Causeway Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
