OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FThe Medical Director of the Northern
OL,7,FTrust, Dr Dave Watkins, said of the
OL,8,Fchange: "We are running two complete
OL,9,Fservices at the moment, which means
OL,10,Fwe've got two relatively small teams
OL,11,Ftrying to run everything.
OL,13,F"That has been a problem in other
OL,14,Ftrusts... We want to if we can avoid a
OL,15,Fsituation were services are
OL,16,Fcollapsing."
