OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FWhile campaigners to save the Causeway
OL,7,FHospital have welcomed a proactive
OL,8,Fapproach to prevent a potential
OL,9,Fcollapse in emergency services, they
OL,10,Fare concerned it is a further erosion
OL,11,Fof services, given the recent
OL,12,Freduction in maternity provision.
OL,14,FThey are also worried about the risk
OL,15,Fof additional travel time in an
OL,16,Femergency and the pressure it could
OL,17,Fput on other hospitals.
