OL,6,FGemma Brolly of SOS Causeway Hospital
OL,7,FCampaign said it is important people
OL,8,Flook beyond the gloss and beyond the
OL,9,Fpresentation. She said: "We know there
OL,10,Fis a lack of trust which has come from
OL,11,Fprevious consultations,.
OL,13,F"we know this done deal phrase comes
OL,14,Fup again and again, but we urge people
OL,15,Fto equip themselves, look at the
OL,16,Fstrategic vision, look at what is
OL,17,Fhappening around us and look at the
OL,18,Fimpact.
OL,20,F"Ask the questions that need asked."
