OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FKevin McMahon, Director of Surgery and
OL,7,FClinical Services with the Northern
OL,8,FTrust, said: "Currently we provide
OL,9,Felective (planned) and emergency
OL,10,Fgeneral surgery at both Antrim and
OL,11,FCauseway and, for a number of reasons,
OL,12,Fthat model cannot be sustained in the
OL,13,Flonger-term.
OL,15,F"Our surgical teams also believe
OL,16,Fchange is needed, and together we have
OL,17,Flooked at how we can create a better
OL,18,Fservice for patients, while delivering
OL,19,Fa safe and responsive general surgery
OL,20,Fservice for the future.
