OL,6,F"Over the last few months, we have
OL,7,Fengaged extensively with key staff to
OL,8,Fwork through the options and identify
OL,9,Fwhat we believe is the best possible
OL,10,Fdelivery model for our patients and
OL,11,Fservice users, and the wider community.
OL,13,F"The proposal we have brought forward
OL,14,Fto our Trust Board, and which will now
OL,15,Fgo out for public consultation, is an
OL,16,Fevidence-based case for change."
