OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,FA review of general surgery within the
OL,7,FNorthern Trust is made necessary by a
OL,8,Fnumber of factors including workforce
OL,9,Fchallenges, which have made it
OL,10,Fincreasingly difficult to maintain the
OL,11,Frequired levels of staffing to deliver
OL,12,Fall aspects of general surgery
OL,13,Fservices across two sites.
OL,15,FAdditionally, new Departmental
OL,16,Fstandards for emergency and elective
OL,17,Fsurgery contained within the
OL,18,FDepartment of Health's 2022 Review of
OL,19,FGeneral Surgery, cannot be fully met
OL,20,Fwithout service reconfiguration.
