OL,6,FGillian Traub, Northern Trust Director
OL,7,Fof Operations, said: "We know that
OL,8,Fthere has been a lot of rumour and
OL,9,Fspeculation around Causeway Hospital's
OL,10,Ffuture since the transformation of our
OL,11,Fmaternity services in 2023; and we
OL,12,Fexpect people will have questions and
OL,13,Fconcerns around further proposed
OL,14,Ftransformation within the Northern
OL,15,FTrust.
