OL,3,CNorthern Trust proposal to move
OL,4,Cemergency services to one hospital
OL,6,F"As outlined in our Vision for
OL,7,FCauseway, it is, and will remain, a
OL,8,Fvital part of our acute hospital
OL,9,Fnetwork, and this proposed
OL,10,Freconfiguration of general surgery
OL,11,Fwon't change that. In fact, we believe
OL,12,Fthis proposal will further strengthen
OL,13,Four case for Causeway Hospital
OL,14,Fbecoming an elective hub for the
OL,15,Fentire North West region ` one of the
OL,16,Fambitions contained within our Vision."
OL,18,FThe 14-week public consultation will
OL,19,Fopen on Friday 23 August until Friday
OL,20,F29 November, 2024.
